description.property_description: Welcome to a spectacular .75-acre estate offering luxurious living and unparalleled amenities! This meticulously maintained property boasts 3, 766 square feet of exquisite living space, including a charming 400 square foot garage apartment, providing ample room for both relaxation and entertainment. Step inside to discover a lavish interior featuring five spacious bedrooms and four elegantly appointed bathrooms, ensuring comfort and privacy for all residents and guests. The home's versatile layout includes a bonus room, ideal for a home office, gym, or media room, catering to your every need. The attention to detail is evident throughout, with premium upgrades such as a central vacuum system for effortless cleaning and a portico with a garage door for added convenience. The recently painted interior exudes a sense of freshness and vitality, while new carpeting adds warmth and sophistication to the living spaces. Primary suite includes an Australian closet with built-ins for storage. Two bedrooms have a jack-&-jill bathroom plan while the 3rd guest bedroom has its own full bathroom. Outdoor enthusiasts will delight in the property's outdoor amenities, including a greenhouse and raised garden beds, perfect for cultivating your own organic produce and enjoying the beauty of nature from the comfort of your own backyard. Sprinkler system has a private well so you won't be bogged down by water restrictions during the spring. Whether you're hosting gatherings with loved ones or simply enjoying quiet moments of relaxation, this estate offers the perfect backdrop for every occasion. Don't miss your chance to experience the epitome of luxury living in this stunning residence. Garage apartment has closet and half bathroom for convenience. Schedule your private tour today and prepare to be captivated by all that this exceptional property has to offer!
